| !Help for Fireworkz
|
| Default to simple text help
Set Fireworkz$HelpFile FireworkzRes:Help.Text
|
| See whether the HTML manuals are installed
| Try generic Fireworkz-Manuals packaged ones
If "<File$Type_FAF>"="" Then Else Set Fireworkz$HelpFile FireworkzManuals:UserGuide.index/htm
|
| Fallback to simple HTML help
If "<File$Type_FAF>"="" Then Else IfThere <Fireworkz$HelpFile> Then Else Set Fireworkz$HelpFile FireworkzRes:Help.HTML.index/html
|
IfThere <Fireworkz$HelpFile> Then Filer_Run <Fireworkz$HelpFile> Else Error Help not found
